  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Efficacy and adverse effects of Benjakul recipe in Treating Primary Osteoarthritis of Knee
      Compared with Diclofenac. This study was designed as double blind, randomized controlled
      trial. Approval from the ethical committee of Human Research Ethics Committee of Thammasat
      University (No: 1 Faculty of Medicine)
